function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	-- Detect if there is an event quest that spawned (event or SMP), and send a user event to move ot the correct phase
	local IDQuest = Hydra.ActorFindNearestActor(idActorPlayer, 9999, false, true, S_Actor_Quest_Proxy)
	idChestLoc = Hydra.ActorFindNearestActor(idActorPlayer, 9999, false, true, ID_CHESTLOC)	

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(IDQuest) then
		Hydra.EventSend("SMP")
	else
		Hydra.EventSend("No_SMP")
	end
end
